задайти вопросы к каждому предложению рассказа о Джеке-Воробье

Hi, what is my name? My name is ...
Is my name Jack-the-Sparrow? Yes, it is.
Whose name is Jack-the-Sparrow? I или me?

How old am I? Am I thirty years old?

What colours are my eyes?
What colour is my hair?
What is black? What is dark?
Are my eyes black?
Is my hair dark?
Whose hair is dark?
Whose eyes are black?

Am I Spanish?
Am I English?
Who is Spanish?
Who is English?
Who is not Spanish?
Who is not English?

What are my favourite colours?
Are my favourite colours blue and black?
Is my favourite colour green?

Am I pirate?
Who is pirate?

What is my business.
Is my business a pillage?

What is a boring thing for me?
Is a peace a boring thing for me?
Whom is peace a boring thing?

I have two friends. - не стал трогать, т.к. нет am/is/are
вообще, какое отличие am/is/are от present indefinite?

Whose names are Elizabeth and Will Turner?
Are their names Elizabeth and Will Turner?

Who is a girl from English high society?
Is she a girl from English high society?
Where is she?

Who is a smith?
Is he a smith?
What is he?

Where is not many pirates?
In what seas are not many pirates?
What are not many in our seas?
Are there not mamy pirates in our seas?

Are there only nine of us?
How many of us?

